creator: Disprz
descriptionHtml:
This app is the blended learning platform by Imarticus to provide engaging interface to registered learners that combines self paced learning, social collaboration and on-line live training for students undergoing certifications from Premium institutes.

Learners can attend live lectures from premium institutes, do home based activities, experience the whiteboard in real time in- class, submit assessments and interact with faculty real time.

This app translates the Imarticus’s vision of a fully digital campus into reality.
descriptionShort: Feed your curiosity and expand your horizons with Imarticus learning App
title: Imarticus

creator: Disprz
descriptionHtml:
The Imarticus Learning App empowers professionals and students to learn highly sought
after skills and become successful business leaders.

Using cutting edge technology and the latest in pedagogical research, we are creating a new age digital learning experience. Our learning environment is designed to maximize
engagement and retention by providing access to a plethora of complementary learning
materials:

Self paced videos
SCORM modules
In-Class presentations
Classroom lecture recordings
Quizzes
Assignments
Additional reading materials
And lots more.

The app translates the Imarticus Learning’s vision of a fully digital campus into reality
